Package: xfce4-pulseaudio-plugin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Panel plugin for controlling output volume of the PulseAudio mixer.
 Xfce4-pulseaudio-plugin is a panel plugin for controlling an audio output 
 volume of the PulseAudio mixer. The volume can be adjusted using keyboard 
 shortcuts, mouse wheel, a slider in a popup menu (todo), or via a linked 
 external audio mixer tool.
